{"arkId":"cl010092009","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010092009","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Mercure \u00e0 cheval sur P\u00e9gase","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Mercure \u00e0 cheval sur P\u00e9gase"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1698 - 1702 (signature)","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [SCULPT] Salle 102 - Cour Marly, Salle 102 - RDC","room":"Salle 102, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau -1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1698,"endYear":1702,"imprecision":"","text":"Fin du XVIIe si\u00e8cle - d\u00e9but du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Coysevox, Antoine","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1720","place":"","type":"date de mort"},{"date":"1640","place":"Lyon","type":"date de naissance"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q505134"},{"label":"France","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"MR 1822","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Sculptures du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"groupe","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; Sur le rocher, \u00e0 la base: \u0022ANTONIUS COYZEVOX LUGD SCUL REG FECIT 1702 \/ LES DEUX GROUPES ONT ESTE FAITES [sic] EN DEUX ANS\u0022","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"3,15","displayDimension":"3,15 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"2,91","displayDimension":"2,91 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"1,28","displayDimension":"1,28 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur avec accessoire","value":"3,26","displayDimension":"3,26 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":6,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"marbre de Carrare","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"parc (France-\u003EMarly) (Abreuvoir)","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Command\u00e9 en 1698 par Jules Hardouin-Mansart (1646-1708), surintendant des B\u00e2timents du roi, et destin\u00e9 avec La Renomm\u00e9e sur P\u00e9gase du m\u00eame sculpteur (voir MR 1824), \u00e0 faire un groupe (en pendant) appel\u00e9 La Renomm\u00e9e du Roi. Destin\u00e9 \u00e0 \u00eatre plac\u00e9 de part et d\u0027autre de la balustrade sup\u00e9rieure du bassin de l\u0027Abreuvoir du parc de Marly. Acomptes pour le mod\u00e8le en pl\u00e2tre, du 21 d\u00e9cembre 1698 au 19 avril 1799. Mod\u00e8les moul\u00e9s par Le Pileur, par contrat du 31 ao\u00fbt 1699. Parfait paiement des mod\u00e8les en pl\u00e2tre, 6 septembre 1699. Blocs de marbre command\u00e9s au marbrier J\u00e9r\u00f4me Derbais, par contrat du 22 juillet 1699, livr\u00e9s au Havre via G\u00eanes, en ao\u00fbt 1700, puis \u00e0 l\u0027atelier du sculpteur, le 13 f\u00e9vrier 1701. Acomptes pour l\u2019ex\u00e9cution du marbre, du 30 janvier 1701 au 17 d\u00e9cembre 1702. Plac\u00e9s dans le parc de Marly, les 2 et 8 ao\u00fbt 1702. D\u00e9tails termin\u00e9s sur place. Parfait paiement, 9 septembre 1703. Transport\u00e9s en juin 1719 \u00e0 l\u0027entr\u00e9e ouest du jardin des Tuileries. Entr\u00e9s au Louvre en janvier 1986.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"entr\u00e9e","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"06\/1719","startYear":1719,"endYear":1719},{"type":"date d\u0027arriv\u00e9e au Mus\u00e9e","value